# Protobuf Conventions

## Package naming

```protobuf
package auth.v1;
```

Import path: `app/{service}/api/{domain}/v1/{service}.proto`

## File structure

```protobuf
syntax = "proto3";
package auth.v1;
import "google/api/annotations.proto";

service AuthService {
  rpc Register(RegisterRequest) returns (RegisterResponse);
}

message RegisterRequest {
  string email = 1;
  string password = 2;
}
```

## Naming rules

- Service: `{Domain}Service` (PascalCase)
- RPC: `{Verb}{Resource}` (PascalCase)
- Request/Response: `{RpcName}Request` / `{RpcName}Response`
- Field: snake_case (proto) → camelCase (Go)
- Enum: `UPPER_SNAKE_CASE`

## HTTP mapping

- Service proto dùng annotations để generate HTTP handler (qua protoc-gen-go-http)
- Auth-service: HTTP port 8080, gRPC port 9090
- Backend service: HTTP port 8000, gRPC port 9000

## Generate

Dùng `buf generate` với cấu hình trong file `buf.gen.yaml` của service.
